ION CRUISERÂ The elevator starts to descend rapidly.Â OBI-WAN: Stop, stop! Artoo, we need to be going up.Â 28 INT. ELEVATOR SHAFT-TRADE FEDERATION CRUISERÂ Anakin struggles to hang on to the narrow edge of the elevator shaft. The door to the elevator shaft is pried open, and TWO BATTLE DROIDS appear in the doorway and look down at ANAKIN. They point their guns at him.Â DROID 1: Hands up, Jedi! Don&#39;t move.Â DROID 2: Roger, roger.Â 29 INT. MAIN HANGAR-TRADE FEDERATION CRUISERÂ The TWO SUPER BATTLE DROIDS overhear OBI-WAN&#39;s comlink messages to ARTOO.Â SUPER BATTLE DROID 1: There it is again.Â OBI-WAN: (OS) Artoo, do you copy? Artoo, do you hear me? Artoo, we need to be going up, not down.Â 30 INT. ELEVATOR-TRADE FEDERATION CRUISERÂ The elevator races down as OBI-WAN holds on.Â OBI-WAN: Stop. Artoo! We need to go up! Stop, stop!Â The elevator stops with a jolt. OBI-WAN falls to the floor.Â 31 INT. MAIN HANGAR-TRADE FEDERATION CRUISERÂ The TWO SUPER BATTLE DROIDS see ARTOO and walk toward the little droid.Â SUPER BATTLE DROID 1: Hey you!Â ARTOO plugs into the interface again and the elevator shoots up.Â 32 INT. ELEVATOR-TRADE FEDERATION CRUISERÂ OBI-WAN stands up after having fallen in the elevator.Â OBI-WAN: Now, that&#39;s better . . .Â 33 INT. MAIN HANGAR-TRADE FEDERATION CRUISERÂ ARTOO is held up by TWO SUPER BATTLE DROIDS, who chuckle as the little Astro Droid curses and swings at them.Â SUPER BATTLE DROID 1: You stupid little astro droid!Â 34 INT. ELEVATOR SHAFT-TRADE FEDERATION CRUISERÂ ANAKIN looks down and sees the elevator heading toward him at a high rate of speed. He looks at the BATTLE DROIDS leaning over him with their guns pointed at him. He calculates for a moment, then gives himself a push and flips himself up into the elevator shaft.Â Before ANAKIN can arc into a descent down the shaft, the elevator races up through the shaft, cutting the DROIDS in two. ANAKIN lands on the elevator and quickly drops back through the hole in the ceiling. OBI-WAN 